11. Deployment

* Local deployment using Flask/FastAPI
* Can be extended to cloud platforms (AWS / Azure)
* Supports containerization using Docker

12. Tools & Technologies

* Python
* Pandas, NumPy
* Scikit-learn
* XGBoost
* Matplotlib, Seaborn
* Flask / FastAPI
* Git & GitHub

13. Results & Conclusion

The system successfully predicts exoplanet habitability with reliable accuracy. Visual and statistical analyses enhance interpretability, making the system suitable for academic demonstrations and real-world extensions.

14. Future Enhancements

* Add deep learning models
* Real-time data integration
* Cloud deployment
* Advanced explainability (SHAP, LIME)


